                    <p rend="flushleft">I <hi rend="italic">Peace Treaty With Italy</hi> (<hi rend="italic">Continuation of discussion</hi>) <hi rend="italic">Article
                            16</hi>.</p>
                    <p>After an exchange of views on the proposals of the Soviet Delegation set
                        forth in <gloss target="#t_CFM46NY1">CFM(46) (NY)</gloss> 13,<note n="12" xml:id="d325fn12"><hi rend="italic">Post</hi>, <ref target="#pg_1156">p.
                                1156</ref>.</note> a decision on this Article was <hi rend="italic">deferred</hi>.</p>
                    <p rend="flushleft">II <hi rend="italic">Next Meeting of the Council</hi></p>
                    <p>Thursday, November 14, at 4:00 p.m.</p>
                    <closer>
